 Robin enquanto este se recupera. Protegido por um velho índio, Grilo põe João em situações ridículas e atrapalha seus planos de casar Catarina com Nepomuceno. Robin Hood retorna, salvando a mocinha e casando com ela. Concluído o trabalho, Zé Grilo retorna a sua querida floresta.","status":"Released","language":"pt","releaseDate":"1974-01-01","year":"1974","runtime":78,"rating":4.3,"voteCount":10,"popularity":0,"certification":null,"genres":["Aventura","Comédia","Família"],"poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pj0Sl8OEtCpQlhoJsCHQb8PMMqh.jpg","posterHD":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pj0Sl8OEtCpQlhoJsCHQb8PMMqh.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/8RtE8DmK4ffdyTjuFKfDOme42qi.jpg","backdropHD":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/8RtE8DmK4ffdyTjuFKfDOme42qi.jpg","logo":null,"cast":[{"id":936457,"name":"Renato Aragão","character":"Zé Grilo","photo":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/qAMsFDbdxId9npuVi5hUuGP1ruL.jpg"},{"id":936458,"name":"Dedé Santana","character":"William","photo":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/9DAtjZjyNFOQurBOJrKrmHiw4fE.jpg"},{"id":1165026,"name":"Monique Lafond","character":"Catarina","photo":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/gBDva8rq8N2iJfox1iGVNG8FCAa.jpg"},{"id":1278928,"name":"Jorge Cherques","character":"Coronel João Climério dos Reis","photo":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/eRZN4gdG95HyVP4DCENqynUr9CP.jpg"},{"id":1266368,"name":"Milton Vilar","character":"Guilherme","photo":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/eDvv9XkiJTnsDNtn40AKUaLOSNS.jpg"},{"id":1618219,"name":"Olívia Pineschi","character":"Isolda","photo":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/s4V00tG9VkL5WUVj54Qbun5KsdI.jpg"},{"id":1168392,"name":"Mário Cardoso","character":"Robin Hood","photo":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/lWfKCHud60QK7QD0emVuxIs62VG.jpg"},{"id":1137615,"name":"Francisco Dantas","character":"Tabelião","photo":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/oVHQGmk39EHEV9IlqSVSAVoZvJ5.jpg"},{"id":1199636,"name":"Paulão","character":"Nepomuceno dos Reis Leão","photo":"ht